Shadowverse Holy Saber /ホーリーセイバー （シャドウバース）

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

Train based on AnyLora model. Training resources include official arts ,leader live2D and some screenshots from the game on NS platform.

Strongly recommend weights from 0.6 to 0.8,and enable hires.fix.

Here's some trigger words you may need to access different costume of the character:

Form 1 (with helmet):alternative1,unevolved,covered eyes,white helmet,white armor,middle blue skirt,(blue sword);

Form 2 (no helmet):alternative2,evolved,hair ornaments,blue eyes,white armor,middle blue skirt,(blue sword);

Form 3 (black,with helmet):alternative3,unevolved,covered eye,black helmet,yellow eye,black armor,middle red skirt,(red sword);

Form 4 (black,no helmet):alternative4,evolved,hair ornaments,yellow eyes,black armor,middle red skirt,(red sword).

Some words like "armor","holding sword(shield)","glowing","star-shaped pupils" might be necessary to enhance the costume,making it more faithful to origin artworks.

Also,you may add"white(black,transparent,simple) background" to negative prompts to avoid those backgrounds caused by L2D trainning materials.

Hope you enjoy this loha:)

Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned (for realistic models & 2,5D), kl-f8-anime2, blessed2.vae (for anime models)

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras or DPM++ 2M Karras

  • Steps: 20 to 35

  • Clipskip: 2

  • Upscaler : img2img in comfyui using 4x-UltraMix_Smooth

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9 (mostly 7 and 8)

  • LORA weight for txt2img: 0.5-1 (for the examples i mostly used 0.8)

  • Denoise strength for img2img: 0.4 to 0.7

If you want the exact same settings, just drag and drop the picture into ComfyUI
